title: KMSpico v10.1.6 Activator For Windows and Office Full
description:
KMSpico v10.1.6 
- Requirements: .NET 4.0 or Windows 8/8.1/10/2012/2016.

- Activate:
Windows Vista Bussines/Enterprise
Windows 7 Professional/Enterprise
Windows 8/8.1/10 All (By Now)
Office 2010/2013/2016 (Theorically)
Windows Server 2008/2008R2/2012/2012R2/2016 (Theorically)


Run KMSpico_setup.exe
Install it.
(Optional) Create a tokens backup with the buttom: Create.
Press the Red Button.
Done.


Change Log
v10.1.6
- Fixed small bugs.
- Improved log details
